packageYml.name: package.yml
packageYml.content:
matches:
  - trigger: "c^"
    replace: "č"
  - trigger: "C^"
    replace: "Č"
  - trigger: "s^"
    replace: "š"
  - trigger: "S^"
    replace: "Š"
  - trigger: "z^"
    replace: "ž"
  - trigger: "Z^"
    replace: "Ž"
